</title><style>
  #scroller {
    overflow: hidden;
    columns: 65535;
    column-fill: auto;
    padding: 32768;
    gap: 0;
    width: 400px;
    height: 100px;
    scroll-marker-group: before;
  }

  #scroller::scroll-marker-group {
    display: flex;
    height: 200px;
    background: gray;
  }

  #scroller>div::scroll-marker {
    display: block;
    width: 1px;
    height: 50%;
    content: "";
    background: yellow;
  }

  fieldset {
    border: 3px solid black;
  }
</style>
<p>There should be a yellow square inside a gray box below, and below that, a
  fieldset with a legend. The text "first" and "second" should be seen
  inside.</p>
